  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/32px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Palm Leaves</b> are a resource in <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Shipwrecked\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Shipwrecked\"><i>Shipwrecked</i></a> DLC. They can be obtained by chopping down <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Palm_Tree\" title=\"Palm Tree\">Palm Trees</a>.\n</p><p>They can be used for several crafting recipes, including <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Backpack#Thatch_Pack\" title=\"Backpack\">Thatch Packs</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Thatch_Sail\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Thatch Sail\">Thatch Sails</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sea_Trap\" title=\"Sea Trap\">Sea Traps</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tropical_Parasol\" title=\"Tropical Parasol\">Tropical Parasols</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Palm_Leaf_Hut\" title=\"Palm Leaf Hut\">Palm Leaf Huts</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wildbore_House\" title=\"Wildbore House\">Wildbore Houses</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Sand_Castle\" title=\"Sand Castle\">Sand Castles</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blubber_Suit\" title=\"Blubber Suit\">Blubber Suits</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Tar_Suit\" title=\"Tar Suit\">Tar Suits</a>.\n</p><p>Palm Leaves are also a rather inefficient source of <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Fuel\" title=\"Fuel\">Fuel</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\">Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Palm_Leaf\" title=\"Palm Leaf\"><img alt=