  "plainText": "Exclusive to:\nPalm Leaf\nFood Info\n10\n10\n0\nWood\n(non-survivor food)\nObject Info\n+1\n15 sec\n40\nSource\nDropped by\n(, , )\nMiscellaneous\n\"palmleaf\"\n鈥淚'm fond of these fronds.鈥漒n鈥揥ilson\n鈥淵ou'll burn.鈥漒n鈥揥illow\n鈥淏ig green leaf.鈥漒n鈥揥olfgang\n鈥淚 bet this leaf mourns its fallen tree.鈥漒n鈥揥endy\n鈥淢ULTI-USE VEGETATION鈥漒n鈥揥X-78\n鈥淚t fell from the palm.鈥漒n鈥揥ickerbottom\n鈥淚 use it for fanning myself.鈥漒n鈥揥oodie\n鈥淣ow I just need servants to fan my glorious self!鈥漒n鈥揗axwell\n鈥淟arge leaf. Sizable fronds. Excellent for construction purposes.鈥漒n鈥揥agstaff\n鈥淎 Viking-sized leaf!鈥漒n鈥揥igfrid\n鈥淏ig leaf.鈥漒n鈥揥ebber\n鈥淲ould make a radical skirt.鈥漒n鈥揥alani\n鈥淭hese would work well in tamales.鈥漒n鈥揥arly\n鈥淲hut can I make wit' this here?鈥漒n鈥揥oodlegs\n鈥淏Y MY LEAF鈥漒n鈥揥ilba\n鈥淲ig from friend hair鈥漒n鈥揥ormwood\n鈥淪o many uses. Projectile being the best one.鈥漒n鈥揥heeler\nPalm Leaves are a resource in Shipwrecked DLC. They can be obtained by chopping down Palm Trees.\nThey can be used for several crafting recipes, including Thatch Packs, Thatch Sails, Sea Traps, Tropical Parasols, Palm Leaf Huts, Wildbore Houses, Sand Castles, Blubber Suits and Tar Suits.\nPalm Leaves are also a rather inefficient source of Fuel.\nUsage[edit | edit source]\n脳4\n脳3\n脳4\n脳6\n脳4\n脳2\n脳4\n脳2\n脳2\n脳4\n脳4\n脳3\n脳5\n脳8\n脳4\n脳2\n脳3\n脳4\n脳2\n脳4\n脳2\n脳2\n脳4\n脳2\nView or edit this template\nResources\nAttention: The following categories are only for the players look up the page based on their first impression, they have nothing to do with the actual categories/behavior/function/tags of these items\nPlants\nNatural non-living materials\nMobs Parts\nSkins\nFeathers\nBones and horns\nGems\nShadow Resources\nLunar Resources\nCraftable Resources\nNon-natural materials\nTrinkets\nLost Relics\nTransmission Items",
